<ul>
<li>Processor&nbsp;- Dual Quad Core 64 bit Intel Xeon at 3.16Ghz and 16GB RAM</li>
<li>Cluster&nbsp;- 128 node, 1024 Processor Cores and 2TB of Memory </li>
<li>Performance&nbsp;- system performance of 9.5 Tera FLOPS. SMP Linpack of each node is 81 GFLOPS</li>
<li>Interconnects&nbsp;- Infiniband 144 DDR 4X 20 Gbps networks and two Gigabit Ethernet networks</li>
<li>Storage&nbsp;- 24 Tera Byte Unified Storage & GlusterFS NUFA distributed storage of 20 TByte</li>
<li>Backup&nbsp;- Automated Tape Library with 4 LTO-3 drives and 48 media slots to backup upto 38.4 TB</li>
<li>Operating System&nbsp;- Red Hat Enterprise Linux 5.1</li>
</ul>
